    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen of automotive preservation. This vehicle is offered in impeccable condition, manifesting a level of care and maintenance that aligns with the highest industry standards. Every facet of this automobile, from its flawless exterior finish to its pristine interior appointments, suggests a history of fastidious ownership. This is a rare opportunity for the sophisticated buyer to secure a vehicle that remains in showroom state, offering both mechanical reliability and aesthetic perfection.",
